{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/LinkMonoComponentTokens-Implementations"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentDisabled","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentEnabled","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentFocus","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentHover","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentPressed"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/linkmonocomponenttokens-implementations"]}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"LinkMonoComponentTokens Implementations","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"collectionGroup","roleHeading":"API Collection"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/monoColorContentFocus":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token MultipleColorSemanticToken(light: colors.repositoryNeutralEmphasizedBlack, dark: colors.repositoryNeutralMutedWhite)"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/monocolorcontentfocus","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentFocus","title":"monoColorContentFocus","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"monoColorContentFocus"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/monoColorContentDisabled":{"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token MultipleColorSemanticToken(light: colors.repositoryOpacityBlackMedium, dark: colors.repositoryOpacityWhiteMedium)","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/monocolorcontentdisabled","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"monoColorContentDisabled","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/monoColorContentDisabled","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"monoColorContentDisabled","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSLink","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"LinkComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","identifie